<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Privacy Policy – QRCraft by Meecro</title>
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css"
  />
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet"
  />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #ffffff;
      --card: #f7f9fc;
      --primary: #1e3a8a;
      --accent: #2563eb;
      --text: #1f2937;
      --subtext: #4b5563;
      --radius: 8px;
      --transition: 0.3s;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    header p {
      color: var(--subtext);
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--card);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
      transition: transform var(--transition), box-shadow var(--transition);
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }

    .card h2 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: var(--subtext);
    }

    .full-width {
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
    }

    .last-updated {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 2rem 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--subtext);
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 3rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--subtext);
    }

    a.button {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background var(--transition);
    }

    a.button:hover {
      background: var(--primary);
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .cards {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>QRCraft Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Your privacy matters. Last updated: May 21, 2025</p>
  </header>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-camera"></i> Camera Access</h2>
        <p>
          We only request camera access to scan QR codes in real time.
          No images or videos are stored or transmitted off your device.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> QR Code Generation</h2>
        <p>
          Data you enter (URLs, text) is processed entirely on-device.
          We never upload your generated codes to our servers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Scan History</h2>
        <p>
          Scan history is stored locally and is optional. You can clear
          it anytime from the app settings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-ad"></i> AdMob &amp; Analytics</h2>
        <p>
          We use Google AdMob for ads. AdMob may collect anonymized data
          (device ID, IP) per Google's policies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card full-width">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          All your data stays on your device unless you explicitly share it.
          We do not sell, share, or transmit personal data to third parties
          beyond advertising needs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card full-width">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-handshake"></i> Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>
          <strong>Google AdMob:</strong> <a class="button" href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank">View Policy</a>
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>ZXing Library:</strong> Open-source QR scanner, no data collection.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card full-width">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-child"></i> Children’s Privacy</h2>
        <p>
          We comply with COPPA. We do not knowingly collect information
          from children under 13.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card full-width">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-sync-alt"></i> Policy Updates</h2>
        <p>
          Any changes will be posted here. Continued use of QRCraft after
          updates means you accept the revised policy.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="last-updated">
      <i class="fas fa-calendar-alt"></i> Last updated May 21, 2025
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>
        Need help? <a href="mailto:c.g.s.hassan.ali@gmail.com">c.g.s.hassan.ali@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
      <p>© 2023 Meecro Development. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
